n\nChanges:\n- Added dedicated test file:\n  - `tests/src/org.codehaus.janino/commons-compiler/3.0.16/src/test/java/org_codehaus_janino/commons_compiler/ClassBodyDemoTest.java`\n- The test invokes `ClassBodyDemo.main(...)` with a class body and argument, reaching:\n  - `Class#getMethod(...)`\n  - `Method#invoke(...)`\n- Added a lightweight `IClassBodyEvaluator` test implementation to avoid real runtime bytecode generation while still exercising the sample’s public flow.\n- Updated `CompilerFactoryFactoryTest.TestCompilerFactory` to provide that evaluator so test ordering does not break the cached default compiler factory.\n\nI did not run tests, per instruction.\n\nNote: `git status` also shows unrelated pre-existing changes in:\n- `tests/src/org.codehaus.janino/commons-compiler/3.0.16/user-code-filter.json`\n- `metadata/org.codehaus.janino/commons-compiler/3.0.16/`", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bbafbe82c6a6a790169f9405376cc81a28a0608928f1d5036\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 756, "output": 843, "cacheRead": 26624, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28223, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777942600595, "responseId": "resp_0bbafbe82c6a6a790169f940494aa481a29a38b0b82dfafffe"}}
